profileText: a Representative from Massachusetts; born in Boston, Suffolk County, Mass., on January 29, 1988; graduated from Newton North High School, Newton, Mass., 2006; A.B., Harvard University, Cambridge, Mass., 2010; M.B.A., Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Cambridge, Mass., 2016; United States Marine Corps, 2010-2015; member of the Newton, Mass., city council, 2016-2020; business professional; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Seventeenth Congress (January 3, 2021-present).
